        <item>
        <title>Links</title>
        <link>https://calabchen.github.io/en/links.html</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://calabchen.github.io/en/links.html</guid>
        <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;my-blog-information&#34;&gt;My Blog Information😎
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: CalabChen&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Introduction: CalabChen’s blog website&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Address: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://calabchen.github.io/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://calabchen.github.io/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Avatar: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://calabchen.github.io/img/avatar_hu535db6adc606d16b32411856b5672cf4_36858_300x0_resize_box_3.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://calabchen.github.io/img/avatar_hu535db6adc606d16b32411856b5672cf4_36858_300x0_resize_box_3.png&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;friend-link-application&#34;&gt;Friend link application🥳
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to apply for a friend link, please leave a message in the comment area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comment area format:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Website name: (required)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Website introduction: (optional)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Website address: (required)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Website avatar: (required)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Format example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;   &lt;/span&gt;- &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;title&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;l&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;l&#34;&gt;GitHub is the world&amp;#39;s largest software development platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;website&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;l&#34;&gt;https://github.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;image&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;l&#34;&gt;https://github.githubassets.com/images/modules/logos_page/GitHub-Mark.png&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;instructions-for-friend-link-exchange&#34;&gt;Instructions for friend link exchange😛
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🎉No plans at the moment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;😩Write it first for fun&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
